title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You might wonder whether you own your things, or they indeed own you. The prospect of losing a valuable possession illuminates how it has become too tied to your self-worth and identity. You may believe an object or an achievement will enhance the meaning and quality of your life. Its easy to get lost when pursuing self-improvement. However, your life is a whole and no single part of yourself can stand on its own. Instead of concentrating on the particulars, focus on the entire field. Youre not rich until you have something money cant buy. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
